  "text": {
    "title": "Animal Photo Day",
    "en": "Today is Animal Photo Day at school. Our classroom is clean, not dirty. On the wall are pictures of animals: a hippo, a zebra, and a goat. Some students bring more photos—bees, frogs, and sheep. We learn new words and write short notes: “The goose is angry,” “The mouse is small,” and “The elephant is strong.” It’s a fun show for our class!",
    "zh": "今天是學校的動物照片日。我們的教室很乾淨，不髒。牆上有很多動物照片：河馬、斑馬和山羊。有些同學帶了更多的照片——蜜蜂、青蛙和綿羊。我們學新單字並寫短註記：「這隻鵝很生氣」、「這隻老鼠很小」、「這頭大象很強壯」。這是我們班的一場有趣的小展覽！"
  },
  "reading": {
    "title": "I Am Bigfoot",
    "en": "I am tall and strong. I am not an elephant. I am brown and hairy, but I am not a bear. The forest is my home. Fruit is my favorite food. Yeti is my good friend. Look! Those are my footprints. They are very big. I am Bigfoot.",
    "zh": "我又高又強壯，但我不是大象。我是棕色、毛茸茸的，但我不是熊。森林是我的家，水果是我最喜歡的食物。雪人是我的好朋友。看！那些是我的腳印，又大又清楚。我是大腳怪。"
  },
  "exercise": {
    "title": "At the Nature Park",
    "en": "This Saturday, our class visits a nature park. We see lions and tigers in pictures but not in the field. Near the pond, a frog jumps. On a bench, we share fruit. I take a photo of a goat and a sheep. My friend points to big footprints on the trail and says, “Maybe Bigfoot is here!” We laugh and follow the clean path back to school.",
    "zh": "這個星期六，我們班去自然公園。野外沒有真的獅子和老虎，只在圖卡上看得到。池塘邊有青蛙跳動；我們坐在長椅上分享水果。我拍到一隻山羊和一隻綿羊。朋友指著步道上又大又清楚的腳印，說：「也許大腳怪在這裡！」我們笑著沿著乾淨的步道走回學校。"
  },
